HEADWORD: Kist
<hw>Kist</hw> <pr>(k⟦icr⟧st)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Chest</er>.]</ety> <def>A chest; hence, a coffin.</def> <mark>[Scot.
& Prov. End.]</mark> <rj><au>Jamieson.</au> <au>Halliwell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

