==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Kist
<hw>Kist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Ar. <ets>gist</ets>.]</ety> <def>A
stated payment, especially a payment of rent for land; hence, the time
for such payment.</def> <mark>[India]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

